Betty Liu  hosts Bloomberg Radio's 
"In the Loop, At the Half," featuring a recap of market action 
since the opening bell, a "drill down" into a top story of the 
day, a "trader radar" interview examining the thoughts of a 
trader on one of the trading floors, and a "four to go" segment 
on the four things listeners should know for the afternoon's 
trading.  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 26:37
 